\(\displaystyle
f(x) = \)\{$a0->ans_rule(3)\} \(+\displaystyle\sum\limits_{n=1}^\infty\Bigg[\)\{$zero->ans_rule\}\(\displaystyle\cos\left(\frac{n\pi x}{$p}\right) +\)\{$bn->ans_rule\}\(\displaystyle\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{$p}\right) \Bigg]\)
